metadata.name: Bull Rider Flight #1
metadata.description:
Kalapootu is a Bull Race conducted in Kerala, India by a farmer's community. It's a big festival here in some parts of Kerala.
In between the competitive junior category bulls and rider runs through the track for training purpose.
This rider couldn't run as fast as the bull and he started to fall down but he tried his maximum to hold on, this effort resulting me with this awesome frame giving a feeling that the rider is flying in the air hence the title "Bull Rider Flight"

CAPTURED WITH NIKON D7500 + NIKON 200-500 MM LENS
CAPTURED AT PALAKKAD, KERALA, INDIA
CAPTURED ON 20 JULY,2022
